works.description: EcoSmart fireplaces never fail to amaze with their modern and eco-friendly designs. And this time around the brand has gone retro with its new fireplace called EcoSmart “STIX” that is inspired by a traditional campfire, but is fueled by bioethanol. The fireplace features varying-sized tubular stainless steel sticks secured around the latest AB3 burner, that can efficiently last in excess of 8 hours with 3 liters of fuel.
